{"tid":2451157,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"法證先鋒V｜落實開拍周柏豪做男主角　編審葉天成：小丑一定會有","createTime":"2021-03-18T01:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T01:49:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f3446f9428796168bae619480117f886d5209516","tid":2451157,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"《法證先鋒V》落實開拍！上年播放的《法證先鋒IV》錄得極好收視，最高達到40點，全劇平均收視36.3點，令到無綫立即決定添食！暫時所知，因頭四輯的監製梅小青退休，所以監製位置由上一輯的執行監製方俊華頂上，而編審的位置，將會是金像獎最佳編劇兼《使徒行者》系列編審葉天成擔任，而知男主角其中一位就知周柏豪。<br />\n<br />\n早前網上傳出，TVB將會開拍一套名為《黑社會》的劇集，主角是周柏豪，編審也是葉天成，不過葉天成在接受《香港01》訪問時表示這部劇他並不存在，自己正在為《法證先鋒V》作準備，他說：「我哋諗過好多題材，我上年都諗過啲類近，6、70年代講香港黑社會、警察嘅戲，曾經有咁樣構思過，構思完之後未正式落實，因為我要開《法證先鋒V》。係稍稍有個構思啫，因為我哋本身會構思好多劇種，睇吓投資方要唔要，或者我哋自己有咩題材可以發展，嗰個暫時hold住咗，冇劇本出過，係傾過吓啲故事大綱。」<br />\n<br />\n講到《法證先鋒》系列，當然不能不提「小丑」這個角色，是頭四輯的監製梅小青特意舖排，在《法證先鋒IV》大結局的一幕，四個小丑的屍體攤在地上，手掌擺出一個五字手勢，大家都猜測是不是為第五輯舖路。而《法證先鋒IV》中張曦雯飾演的角色，童年也是被小丑擄走，導致有陰影，最終成為final boss。<br />\n<br />\n葉天成也有為小丑這個設定解畫，並表示新一輯繼續會有這個角色，他說：「小丑呢個設計係一至四輯都有，亦都係小青姐一個好有追看性、懸疑性嘅設計，我哋一定會保留，因為方俊華都跟咗小青姐起碼做咗三輯，佢有問過，我話一定會有，我亦都好尊重小青姐。不過可能會有特別小小嘅小丑出場，例如可能係西片嘅小丑？我哋仲考慮緊，因為我哋嘅劇本仲創作緊，當然希望有啲新嘅元素畀觀眾睇。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201018/394469845065797632541309.jpeg/Kmi_VlxkBeEz9HDwNXtBGQVuGSn-0zx4-QeRwPkHkcA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201018%2F394469845065797632541309.jpeg%2FKmi_VlxkBeEz9HDwNXtBGQVuGSn-0zx4-QeRwPkHkcA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=dec1f11d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4019298/org/6eba933a0bd92258ca30218a10fb0771.jpg/0dmC0_NgWdfFGV0jgYeNI67XWAPen7ruCoreoAqK3qA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4019298%2Forg%2F6eba933a0bd92258ca30218a10fb0771.jpg%2F0dmC0_NgWdfFGV0jgYeNI67XWAPen7ruCoreoAqK3qA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=dd32cb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210317/448975080790167552416852.jpeg/VIleW72hi7ReEhzEo1pjb8zfLRE4J86vcKbuznCm7s4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210317%2F448975080790167552416852.jpeg%2FVIleW72hi7ReEhzEo1pjb8zfLRE4J86vcKbuznCm7s4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f569bd6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉天成（圖左）是資深編劇。"},{"pid":"c14e93f6249ca5b5c2886da302239d85563735b1","tid":2451157,"uid":364182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰張仲以為係王晶"},{"pid":"787b039026f702a5e12059d126bd91f9e004ecb1","tid":2451157,"uid":182930,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"3已經唔好睇啦<br />\n4仲廢，仲好意思拍5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35ea071543e42bd67cbab45cdcf82138ee1e2b5","tid":2451157,"uid":33514,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"全劇 死因無可疑 搞掂啦<br />\n法醫有用既咩？"},{"pid":"d700fb4c5bb516fd49fefadbf969b7db32d43402","tid":2451157,"uid":2784,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"成班已經係小丑啦"},{"pid":"97ec63c7952b980fcbebe47e0381e82a2707bf5d","tid":2451157,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d700fb4c5bb516fd49fefadbf969b7db32d43402","tid":2451157,"uid":2784,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"成班已經係小丑啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />